title: Going Back To School Soon? Your New Home Is Ready!
posting_body: ['Welcome Back to School', 'Where Modern Denver Living Meets Comfort', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Bear Valley Park', '5775 W Dartmouth Ave, Denver, CO, 80227', 'Want more info?', 'See the link below:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath', 'Say hello to Bear Valley Park, a mecca for fun and adventure with a twist of modern comfort.', 'Our Denver, CO, apartments for rent sit in the center of an unbeatable location – close to scenic hiking and biking trails and just minutes from all your daily needs.', 'Garden-style grounds welcome you home each day, while phenomenal features and community amenities allow for a life of style and ease.', 'Let us be the first to welcome you to the Southwest Bear Valley Park neighborhood.', 'Features', '- Microwave', '- In-Home Washer & Dryer', '- Gas Fireplace*', '- Refrigerator with Ice Maker', '- Stainless-Steel Appliances', '- Kitchen Islands*', '- Dishwasher', '- Spacious Private Balcony or Patio', '- Walk-In Closets*', '- Air Conditioning', '- Vaulted Ceilings*', '*In Select Homes', 'Community Amenities', '- 24-Hour Fitness Center', '- Clubhouse', '- Outdoor Fire Pit', '- Great Location Off Highway 285', '- Parking Lot with Available Garages', '- Heated Swimming Pool', '- Bark Park', '- Onsite Maintenance', '- Easy Access to Hiking & Biking Trails', '- Business Center', '- Community BBQ Grills', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:10:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Prices are subject to change, based on availability and qualification of the applicant, additional fees may apply.', 'g5HIxCqJ']
